                                    <h3 class="eb-item__title">
                                        <a href="/news/stay-or-go-jakartas-coastal-communities-mull-adaptation-or-migration-as-the-city-sinks/" class="eb-item__link">
                                            Stay or go? Jakarta&#8217;s coastal communities mull adaptation or migration as the city sinks
                                        </a>
                                    </h3>
                                </div>
                                <div class="eb-item__standfirst">
                                    
                                    
                                        As Indonesia&#x27;s capital is slowly claimed by the Java Sea, thousands of people are losing their homes and …
                                    
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <a href="/news/stay-or-go-jakartas-coastal-communities-mull-adaptation-or-migration-as-the-city-sinks/" class="u-faux-block-link__overlay" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">Stay or go? Jakarta&#x27;s coastal communities mull adaptation or migration as the city sinks</a>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                
                    <li class="eb-item eb-item--has-image eb-item--list--media-square-mobile eb-item--list-media-square-tablet eb-item--section-news eb-item--news-small">
                        <div class="eb-item__container">
                            <div class="eb-item__media-wrapper">
