                                    India Prime Minister Narendra Modi forged the alliance to demonstrate the country&#x27;s climate leadership as host of the G20 summit. India is betting on blended fuels to help displace coal and oil.
                                
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/news/explainer-what-is-the-global-biofuel-alliance/" class="u-faux-block-link__overlay" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">Explainer: What is the Global Biofuel Alliance?</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            
                <div class="eb-item eb-item--has-image eb-item--list-media-mobile eb-item--standard-tablet eb-item--news" data-item-num="4">
                    <div class="eb-item__container">
                        <div class="eb-item__media-wrapper">
                            <div class="eb-item__image-container u-responsive-ratio u-responsive-ratio--hd">
                                


