                                <h3 class="eb-item__title">
                                    <a href="/news/explaining-the-philippines-writ-of-kalikasan-what-does-the-special-legal-remedy-mean-for-nature-protection/" class="eb-item__link">
                                        Explaining the Philippines’ ‘writ of kalikasan’: What does the special legal remedy mean for nature protection?
                                    </a>
                                </h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="eb-item__standfirst">
                                
                                    A most recent case involves the Supreme Court issuing the nature writ to stop mining firms from operating in Palawan. Eco-Business looks into this unique mechanism under Philippine environmental law that gives the people constitutional right to a healthy environment.
                                
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/news/explaining-the-philippines-writ-of-kalikasan-what-does-the-special-legal-remedy-mean-for-nature-protection/" class="u-faux-block-link__overlay" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">Explaining the Philippines’ ‘writ of kalikasan’: What does the special legal remedy mean for nature protection?</a>
